Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libfaad2-0 (= ${Source-Version}), libc6-dev | libc-dev
Replaces: libfaad2-0 (<< 2.0.0clean-0ubuntu2)
Description: freeware Advanced Audio Decoder - development files
 FAAD2 is the fastest ISO AAC audio decoder available. FAAD2 correctly
 decodes all MPEG-4 and MPEG-2 MAIN, LOW, LTP, LD and ER object type AAC
 files.
 .
 This package contains development files.

Package: libmp4v2-0
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Replaces: libmp4, libmp4-0
Conflicts: libmp4, libmp4-0
Description: MP4 container library - runtime files
 FAAD2 is the fastest ISO AAC audio decoder available. FAAD2 correctly
 decodes all MPEG-4 and MPEG-2 MAIN, LOW, LTP, LD and ER object type AAC
 files.
 .
 This package contains runtime files of the optional library for
 accessing MP4 files. Needed by the player plugins.

